0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"死獌狗惱羞😂"},{"pid":"62c61621c847fa5a0421cd6126b34ab5bfd4b1aa","tid":748387,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"第一時間諗起個個會員黑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040f83fb66d650e3f7a2de2abeb03effe4fad7a5","tid":748387,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"畫畫？袁生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f850c6998683d1811773a030d49e88b0ba51173","tid":748387,"uid":187004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"睇星島啦，大部分人無時間可以去聽審，但蘋果好多單類似嘅案都講啲唔講啲。<br />\n<br />\n搞到好多人睇完蘋果就懷疑啲女係老屈。明明有幾單證據好足，最後陪審團都判條仔。<br />\n但蘋果可以寫一啲唔寫一啲，搞到成日要連登神探出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返今次係分別兩個女仔，兩個唔同時間被呢條友搞。<br />\n如果好似我咁炒散或無嘢做，認住案件編號去聽一次，就會知點解我會插蘋果啲新聞（因為唔係淨止呢一單報導得勁差）<br />\n<br />\n（btw ，星島個記者都打錯咗少少關於邊度食飯同上屋企嘅時間線，大家睇完下面link 腦補返個時間線啦....）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/769837-香港-【涉強姦禁錮】被告曾自稱王者形容父母為狗+受害人作供：好似人格分裂\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F769837-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E6%B6%89%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%9B%BE%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E7%8E%8B%E8%80%85%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E7%88%B6%E6%AF